    {
      "Text": "Security update for mozjs115",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for mozjs115 fixes the following issues:\n\nChanges in mozjs115:\n\n- CVE-2026-32776: Fixed a NULL pointer dereference when processing empty external parameter entities inside an entity declaration value (bsc#1259728)\n- CVE-2026-32777: Fixed a denial of service due to infinite loop in DTD content parsing (bsc#1259713)\n- CVE-2026-32778: Fixed a NULL pointer dereference in 'setContext' on retry after an out-of-memory condition (bsc#1259731)\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
